💡 CPENT Exam Tips
If SSH available → use SSH tunneling
If no SSH but outbound allowed → use CHISEL
If you want full subnet → use SSHUTTLE
If Meterpreter session → autoroute + socks
Always combine:
SOCKS → Proxychains → Nmap


⚠️ Common Mistakes (Exam Killers)
Forgetting -N in SSH
Not configuring proxychains.conf
Using -sS scan (won’t work via proxychains) → use -sT
Wrong IP direction (attacker vs pivot confusion)
